snippet.title: [RM2k] [BR] Rhygar e os Soldados do Rei Walkthrough (No Commentary) Part 2
snippet.description:
Hello guys it`s me again. 
This time I bring to you a comedy brazilian game called `Rhygar and the King`s Knights `. It is a really simple and funny RTP game and one of the first well known (in the brazilian RPGMaker community that is)  RPGMaker games.
